tool_description: Our API generates a complete meal plan that is specific to the nutrition counseling world. We create fully detailed, personalized meal plans with specific ingredients / quantities and little cooking skill required. For better flexibility, our ingredient replacement algorithm creates a template where users can adapt their menu even more to fit their desires.

api_list.name: get-ingredients
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://bespoke-diet-generator.p.rapidapi.com/ingredients"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "bespoke-diet-generator.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
